    <div class="forum-post-panel-main clear-block">
      
      <div class="forum-post-content">
        <p>Not paying for hotel will reduce your main costs.  I assume that you are Vietnamese and can stay with some family.</p>
<p>Bring $10-$15 per day for food and drinks (you don't drink, but still you will want coffee or sinh to or other refreshments throughout the day, and you could also spend just $5 on food if you want) and anything else is discretionary.</p>
<p>Of course, you should have some emergency cash.</p>
      </div>

      
