          <span class="forum-in-reply-to"><a href="cost-living-vietnam-its-really-cheap.html#comment-125" class="active">(Reply to #37)</a></span>
    
        
    <span class="forum-post-number"><a href="cost-living-vietnam-its-really-cheap2679.html?page=1#comment-127" class="active">#144</a></span>
