<p>Expect to get ripped off for small amounts daily, to be harassed by taxi drivers, and to be cheated by police at some point. &nbsp;I can guarantee you will lose a phone and your purse will be snatched at least once (probably by a guy on a scooter) and it's a 50% chance your home will be broken into.</p>
<p>It's not safer than most countries, just most developing countries...</p>      </div>

      
