I dont know how it costs you so little. A beer at a club is 5usd already and its hard not to go out every nite.<br />
By the way my house in D1 is for rent. The link is here http://goo.gl/YUnw Email me <a href="../cdn-cgi/l/email-protection.html" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="472920323e22292f23263307202a262e2b6924282a">[email&#160;protected]</a> if you are interested</p>
